schemaVersions.content:
<?xml version = "1.0" encoding = "UTF-8"?>
<xs:schema xmlns:xs = "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
<xs:import namespace="http://www.fixm.aero/flight/4.2" schemaLocation="../../core/flight/Flight.xsd"/>
   <xs:element name = "contact">
      <xs:complexType>
            <xs:element name = "flightNo" type = "xs:string" />
            <xs:element name = "noOfPax" type = "xs:int" />
            <xs:element name = "noOfBaggage" type = "xs:int" />
      </xs:complexType>
   </xs:element>
</xs:schema>
